title: Explain map of European territory in North America

content.question:
Using the map answer (a), (b), and (c).

Briefly explain how ONE specific historical event or development contributed to the changes in land claims depicted in the map.

Briefly explain ONE specific effect of the changes in land claims depicted in the map in the period from 1763 to 1775.

Briefly explain ANOTHER specific effect of the changes in land claims depicted in the map in the period from 1763 to 1775.
